# Build & CI

## Prerequisites

- .NET SDK 10.0.103 (pinned in `global.json`)
- CSharpier tool: `dotnet tool restore`

## Local Development

```bash
dotnet tool restore       # restore CSharpier
dotnet build              # build all projects
dotnet test               # run all tests
dotnet csharpier .        # format all files
dotnet csharpier check .  # verify formatting (CI does this)
```

## CI Pipeline (GitHub Actions)

### PR Validation (`.github/workflows/PR.yml`)
Runs on PRs to `main`: format check → build → test

### Deploy (`.github/workflows/github-pages.yml`)
Runs on push to `main`: test → publish Blazor WASM → deploy to GitHub Pages

### Composite Action (`.github/workflows/steps/action.yml`)
Shared steps: setup .NET SDK → `dotnet tool restore` → `dotnet csharpier check .` → install wasm-tools workload → `dotnet test`

## Package Management

- **Central Package Management** via `Directory.Packages.props`
- Add package versions there, reference without version in `.csproj` files
- Global build properties in `Directory.Build.props`

## No Solution File

This repo has no `.sln` file. Open the folder directly in your IDE. The `Directory.Build.props` applies settings to all projects.
